Narrator: As your boat sails down the glassy surface of the Amazon, you take out the Archbishop's letter's letter. 
Narrator: ‘Father Francisco Xavier, your presence is required at the Rio de Diamantina village. On behalf of the church, we task you with providing spiritual guidance to our flock there. Go with God’ 
Narrator: You tuck the letter away and admire the scenery as a stunning pink dolphin crests the surface of the water next to your boat, as if welcoming you.
